
For Rails 5.2

In json_web_token.rb
Change:   HMAC_SECRET = Rails.application.secrets.secret_key_base
To:   HMAC_SECRET = Rails.application.credentials.secret_key_base

Then run:
$ EDITOR="atom --wait" rails credentials:edit

If this errors
$ rails db:drop
$ rm credentials.yml.enc
$ rm master.key

Then run:
$ EDITOR="atom --wait" rails credentials:edit again